    "section_timeline_UWNLU6": {
      "type": "section-timeline",
      "blocks": {
        "timeline_99cjPc": {
          "type": "timeline",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/olive_colour_boho_dress_with_ledder_sides_see_through_dress_women_by_aya_sacred_wear_3.jpg",
            "subheading": "Commitment One",
            "title": "Sustainable Materials",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-medium",
            "text": "<p>Made in the very heart of beautiful Bali island by loving hands of local artisans. </p><p>AYA especially focus on fabrics that are hand-spun and hand-woven, supporting ancient skills and traditional crafts. Thriving to go deeper to the source of all the materials - from the seed planted to the people who weave the fabric. Our vision is to be able to connect with each being involved in the making from the very source.</p><p>Being able to Source the most ethical, fair trade, Eco and conscious materials.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_type": "btn--primary",
            "button_size": "",
            "button_style": "btn--solid",
            "show_arrow": false,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "timeline_NYeDtL": {
          "type": "timeline",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_4534.jpg",
            "subheading": "Commitment Two",
            "title": "giving back",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-medium",
            "text": "<p>All AYA Sacred Wear production is rooted in Bali.</p><p>We collaborate closely with local artisans, family-run workshops, and village communities — from handwoven fabrics and natural dyeing to handcrafted accessories and finishing details.</p><p><br/></p><p>By producing locally, we actively support livelihoods, preserve traditional skills, and contribute to the wellbeing of the communities behind each piece.</p><p>Every garment carries the hands, stories, and care of the people who create it — transforming craftsmanship into a shared, living exchange.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_type": "btn--primary",
            "button_size": "",
            "button_style": "btn--solid",
            "show_arrow": false,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "timeline_y4X6cW": {
          "type": "timeline",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_4537.jpg",
            "subheading": "Commitment Three",
            "title": "aya community",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-medium",
            "text": "<p>We witness AYA Sacred Wear traveling across the world — adorning the planet through weddings, sacred ceremonies, meaningful gatherings, and unforgettable encounters.</p><p>It is a profound miracle for us to see our creations become part of life’s most important moments.</p><p>To dress this planet, to accompany love, celebration, and connection, is our greatest honor.</p><p><br/></p><p>AYA Sacred Wear is a living community, and we are always open to conscious collaborations, shared visions, and creative exchanges.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_type": "btn--primary",
            "button_size": "",
            "button_style": "btn--solid",
            "show_arrow": false,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "timeline_99cjPc",
        "timeline_NYeDtL",
        "timeline_y4X6cW"
